-- Russian January Capital Flight Reached $17 Billion, Klepach Says
-- B y   I l y a   A r k h i p o v
-- 2012-02-20T10:45:02Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-20/russian-january-capital-flight-reached-17-billion-klepach-says.html
Russian capital outflow reached
about $17 billion last month and inflows may resume in February
or March, Deputy Economy Minister  Andrei Klepach  told reporters
today in the Far East city of Komsomolsk-on-Amur.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ilya Arkhipov in Moscow at 
